<div class="jobview-container">
  <header>
  <div class="back-to-results"><a href="javascript:history.back();"><span class="icon-arrow-left"></span> back to results - 18px</a></div>
  <div class="job-heading">
    <img src="http://placekitten.com/600/600">
    <div class="info">
      <div class="job-title"><%= @job.title %></div>
      <div class="company-name"><%= @job.company.name %></div>
      <div class="city-province"><%= @job.location %></div>
      <div class="posted-when"><%= (@job.created_at).strftime("%d %b %y") %></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>


<div class="job-description">
  <div class="navigation top">
    <a class="prev" href="javascript:history.back();"><span class="icon-arrow-left"></span> previous - 18px</a>
    <a class="next" href="javascript:history.forward();">next <span class="icon-arrow-right"></span></a>
  </div>

  <div class="copy">
    <p>Team Lead, Field Sales (Contract - 12 months)</p>
    <p>Information on Division/Hiring Department/Career Opportunity:</p>
    <p>Bell Canadaâ€™s Field Sales team is looking for a highly motivated and sales driven individual to assume the role of Team Lead, Field Sales.  The objective is to drive RGU growth and penetration within MDU (multi-dwelling unit) and SFU (single family unit) Markets through sales leadership, development and coaching of a team of Field Sales Representatives.</p>
    <p>The successful candidate will be responsible for performance management of the field sales team, development and assignment of key growth territories, ongoing recruitment 
of new sales representatives, sales management, field training and consumer level support.</p>
    <p>Further, this candidate will be responsible for assessing, analyzing and tracking performance to plan, coordinating with cross functional marketing groups and developing 
strong take to market plans and enablers to ensure optimal Field sales success, RGU growth and penetration. </p>
    <p>Job Duties/Accountabilities</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Manage a team of field sales representatives located across the Southwestern Ontario 
  and Golden Horseshoe region.
      <li>Hiring of new sales representatives
      <li>Tracking and analyzing sales trends relative to target.
      <li>Manage the territory of MDU/SFUs and ensure full coverage
      <li>Identify the sales enablers required.
      <li>Provide market intelligence to Account Executives and Marketing
      <li>Track and evaluate budgets and costs of field managers.
      <li>Additional duties as required.
    </ul>
    <p>Critical Qualifications/Competencies:</p>
    <ul> 
      <li>This position requires a minimum of 2-5 years experience in leading a sales team.
      <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills.
      <li>Excellent organizational skills.
    </ul>
    <p>Preferred skills/competencies:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Knowledge of the Telecommunications Industry.
      <li>Experience with the MDU Market.
      <li>Proficiency in PC software applications (Word, Excel, PowerPoint and Adobe)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="navigation bottom">
    <a class="prev" href="javascript:history.back();"><span class="icon-arrow-left"></span> previous - 18px</a>
    <a class="next" href="javascript:history.forward();">next <span class="icon-arrow-right"></span></a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="secondary-content">
  <div class="worko-box job-details">
    <h2 class="worko-heading">h2. sidebar 18px</h2>
    <div class="job-type">
      <label>Job Type:</label>
      <span>Full Time</span>
    </div>
    <div class="job-type">
      <label>Career Level:</label>
      <span><%= @job.career_level %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="job-type">
      <label>Education:</label>
      <span><%= @job.education %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="job-type">
      <label>Job Function:</label>
      <span><a href="#sales-and-business-development"><%= @job.category %></a></span>
    </div>
    <a class="btn2 btn-xlrg apply-now" href="#apply_now">Apply Now</a>
  </div>
  <div class="worko-box social-links">
    <h2 class="worko-heading">h2. sidebar 18px</h2>
    <span class="icon-facebook"></span>
    <span class="icon-linkedin"></span>
    <span class="icon-twitter"></span>
    <span class="icon-email"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="worko-box recent-jobs">
    <h2 class="worko-heading">h2. sidebar 18px</h2>
    <ul class="recent-job-list">
    <% 3.times do |i| %>
      <li class="recent-job">
        <div class="job-title"><a href="#job-title-<%=i+1%>">Job Title # <%=i+1%> - 14px (Hyperlink)</a></div>
        <div class="company-name"><%= @job.company.name %></div>
        <div class="city-province"><%= @job.location %></div>
      </li>
    <% end %>
    </ul>
    <a class="call-to-action" href="#call-to-action">Call to action - 14px &raquo;</a>
  </div>
</div>
</div>